Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁静的村庄是座大佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件 汽车都在暴走状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清事实真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.31,0:00:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.21,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.20,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小兰还有毛利叔叔坐着怀旧的卡扭特汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去影楸村旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.91,0:01:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在途中 车上发生了杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是反对卡扭特车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改为观光用的领导奥村助役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.42,0:02:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在村里警察把赞成派的嫌疑人矢部带去询问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对立的行动发生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.83,0:02:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵涉到七年前的汽车事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在村子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推行观光的船木村长在神社被攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰也有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十位乘客（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.02,0:02:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 有没有伤到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 只是被推倒而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.53,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 那里好像有人晕倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船木村长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀刺穿心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.01,0:02:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐 看见凶手了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能肯定是不是凶手 有人撞了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的人 身材呢 外貌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年团团长矢部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.73,0:03:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 矢部把船木村长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 还没证实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去他家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主管机关来了通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查员到达村子之前停止一切搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.81,0:03:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰差点也和船木村长一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 矢部出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生还没应门呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢部投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮箱里还装着晚报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没回家过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说在警局询问结束释放他后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上约村长并杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划很周密啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.22,0:04:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 搜查附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.22,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 存折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前开始每月存20万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没存在邮局或农业银行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些钱也许是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天为了搜查逃走的矢部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定搜山追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是一样 侦探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 参加这次搜捕不是协助你的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不能让危险的家伙逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里人也协助搜捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两派的队伍调整了对立的态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手希望村人陷入混乱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 有其它意图吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的凶手真的是矢部先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果计划犯罪他会拿走存折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有疑点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄掉菜盘的驹井小姐惧怕的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 赶到慰灵碑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷看的塔子小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部杀人事件的起因是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前发生的车祸案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.52,0:05:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 毁掉村长委托100万的矢部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要抓到那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 新一啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生大案了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮查一下七年前发生的车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那要查看报社网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.92,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有希望了 还我100万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前…七年前…找到了 在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车坠落 乘客两人死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八人重轻伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有记载乘员乘客的姓名吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 死亡报道 所以全部记载了姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.91,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先说轻伤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我抓住了 矢部 认命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 我什么也没做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 逃跑就是杀人的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢部 作为杀人嫌疑犯 你被捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没记载奥村助役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许 奥村助役…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 死掉的两个人名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.21,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手琢祥 28岁 和森次幸平 55岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 请马上查两人的家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到神社里船木村长的叫喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急忙过去的时候你女儿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的情况 我肯定被怀疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然害怕 逃跑时撞了你女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 为什么去那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船木村长叫我过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑生乎乎没有人的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.82,0:08:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说原因 我们很难相信你是无罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你家发现的存折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前开始每月存进20万日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是农业银行 也不是邮局存折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存钱的银行地点不在村里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.41,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这些钱不想让村里人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泄漏了情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做反对派的间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车里被杀的反对派领导奥村助役给我的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把船木村长的动向和想法告诉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.20,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么奥村助役要这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始新项目开发后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里就要投资船木村长的协商公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥村助役他们反对派的协商公司就会被淘汰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前决定破坏计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.32,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 事情已经被船木村长知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.13,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就算我再怎么能言善辩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船木村长在我家里发现了存折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 杀奥村助役是断绝关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀船木村长是因为暴露了对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是 不是我杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的问题好吗 驹井小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.03,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连续杀人案凶手的动机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是村里对立而引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是和七年前的汽车事故有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前 不会吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说凶手不是矢部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为凶手的目标是在七年前那辆车上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是驹井小姐 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事 在汽车里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是七年前汽车事故的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.61,0:10:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以船木村长害怕查明实情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就出100万委托叔叔结束此案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出车祸的消息 报纸上登了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…什么 是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹井小姐 发生过车祸的汽车几点开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车的话 已经出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 驹井小姐 快追公共汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让那个人继续犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托及时赶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 刹车失灵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.92,0:12:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.42,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里开始下坡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢部先生是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.51,0:12:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好像下午上报上级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 爸爸的工作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能得到100万 白干了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 单纯的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来柯南去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾田 怎么开的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用发动机减速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨门式刹车失灵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共汽车的刹车失灵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驹井小姐 和公共汽车并开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳进公共汽车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个跟七年前的事情一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 也是同样的乘客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.11,0:13:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某人告诉了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.62,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前大家也乘过这辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀的船木村长也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和被当作犯人抓起来的青年团团长矢部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部十个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生的事情还记得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把此事讲给我听的驹井小姐是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的汽车导游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.81,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 一起喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不好意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们阻止他 拜托 救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 太过分了 别让她难堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 破坏我们愉快的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逗人笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.61,0:14:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事故中死的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调戏她的男人和出来帮她的乘客两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有八个受伤的村人得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 大家的嘴都被堵住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故原因由两个人的争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说成了两个人喝酒闹事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见死不救的罪恶感埋在心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这里 大家明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次连续杀人案的凶手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.11,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的见义勇为的森次幸平的后人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机是复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.22,0:15:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 塔子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目是跟了母亲姓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名是森次塔子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.93,0:15:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 塔子小姐是 那个乘客的后人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀奥村助役和船木村长的凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公共汽车里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 真凶是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.31,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 公共汽车刹车失灵 横冲直撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 马上报告上级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 你家孩子在公共汽车里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 柯南 怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐为了打听爸爸的死因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.80,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住进了村里 调查不久就查明了真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为同事的关系马上就原谅了司机尾田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇对象之一的矢部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.51,0:16:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵涉到村里的对立的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为是连续杀人案的嫌疑犯被捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐事先知道剩下的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了购物或上班坐这车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此在刹车上动的手脚 计划谋杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在七年前发生车祸的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧 塔子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要装傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还这么冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟大家同归于尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个拐角时速度会减慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话 下车只会受轻伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.11,0:17:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是承认自己的罪行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.41,0:17:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是我杀了奥村助役和船木村长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车内混乱时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奥村助役的水壶里注射了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗中 我在神社捅了村长一刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.70,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是对七年前坐在这车里的全部人复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸比别人富有正义感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然的帮助解决耍酒疯的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.11,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那时候没有一个人站出来帮助爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快逃出去 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.22,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我逃出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.92,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子小姐你还是杀错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.93,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一被害者的奥村助役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前车祸时没乘这辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车导游的你 每天能和他见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该记得的吧 口头禅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年的老座位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果问也七年前的事情会有什么反应呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.72,0:18:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 跟本人确认过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前 一定乘过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就坐了自己的座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他清楚的承认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那天奥村助役得了感冒发烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.61,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报纸没登他的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假…假的 报纸我也看过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的自信害死了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.12,0:19:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 第十位乘客呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十位乘客两年前病发过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.33,0:19:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥村助役和塔子父亲的死根本没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原谅了驹井小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.02,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那情景后无法下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是驹井小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过车祸事故的所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着无法说出的寄托十字架的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 塔子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.01,0:20:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 没勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你相信 希望你原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.32,0:20:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这种情况保持下去到事故的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要像塔子小姐的父亲一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 柯南是无辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要想办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无能为力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拐过下一个弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐不了事故现场的弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没到最后不能放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟 开到沟里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这速度要飞出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士发明的形状记忆材料制成的伸缩带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不能再拉长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.00,0:21:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.40,0:21:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.01,0:21:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件已经解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.01,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在卡扭特汽车又恢复正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们忘记过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.82,0:23:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情享受自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.02,0:23:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底跟谁争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.73,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.20,0:24:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 死了很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.31,0:24:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人进入过这房间 我是证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.51,0:24:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.51,0:24:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑天使的翅膀（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.62,0:24:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.02,0:24:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.12,0:24:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集也是动画原创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说犯人也是原创
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.13,0:24:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.84,0:00:21.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好不同 脚程与表达的方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.49,0:00:37.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我们在两人的记忆中正在渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摸索过 却开始探寻其他人与未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.29,0:00:52.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比自己想象的活得更坚强 追寻一种特别的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.43,0:00:56.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为难以应付的每一天所苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再迷惑 请别松开你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.33,0:01:13.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是互相伤害的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:21.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一直在迷惘的时空中找寻答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.69,0:01:27.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}朝着下一个舞台 you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.41,0:01:39.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,720)}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.34,0:22:19.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什么方式表达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.01,0:22:26.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能让你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.75,0:22:35.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那次以后 不知多少个季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.70,0:22:41.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.67,0:22:49.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是笑着守候在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.34,0:22:59.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢告诉我的事情 还有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.85,0:23:04.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret of my heart 并不是怀疑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.76,0:23:10.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何时 只要还有少许未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:15.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相一定会落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.94,0:23:22.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再说什么 只有等到机会
